@startuml

title Web Admin Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant View
participant Controller
database Database

== Login Process ==
User -> View: Access Login Page
View -> Controller: GET /Account/Login
Controller -> View: Return Login Form
User -> View: Enter Username/Password
View -> Controller: POST /Account/Login
Controller -> Database: Query TAIKHOAN
Database --> Controller: Return User Info
alt Valid Credentials
    Controller -> Controller: Set Session
    Controller -> View: Redirect to Home/Admin
else Invalid
    Controller -> View: Show Error
end

== Order Management Flow ==
User -> View: Access Order List
View -> Controller: GET /OrderAdmin/Index
Controller -> Database: Load HOADON (Include KHACHHANG)
Database --> Controller: Returns List
Controller -> View: Display Table

User -> View: Update Order Status
View -> Controller: POST /OrderAdmin/UpdateStatus
Controller -> Database: Update HOADON.TRANGTHAI
Database --> Controller: Success
Controller -> View: Redirect to Details

@enduml
